Acceleor Profils Infos Extension:
Tool to improve productivity of agents by helping them getting profils informations from profils links.
The tool is using a list of profils links, and outputs infos for each profile in a table, that is available for download.
The format of the table is user friendly.
This tool was created as a collaboration between ACCELEOR and PRF Development.
